Class CK_KEY_DERIVATION_STRING_DATA

java.lang.Object

public class CK_KEY_DERIVATION_STRING_DATA
extends java.lang.Object

class CK_KEY_DERIVATION_STRING_DATA holds a byte string and the byte string's length. It provides the parameters for the CKM_CONCATENATE_BASE_AND_DATA, CKM_CONCATENATE_DATA_AND_BASE, and CKM_XOR_BASE_AND_DATA mechanisms.

PKCS#11 structure: 

  typedef struct CK_KEY_DERIVATION_STRING_DATA {  
    CK_BYTE_PTR pData;  
    CK_ULONG ulLen;  
  } CK_KEY_DERIVATION_STRING_DATA;
